<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Auburn Bay</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Boasting of some of the most idyllic lakeside homes in all of the Southeast Calgary, Auburn Bay is a recently developed suburban neighborhood that is bounded by the Stoney Trail on the north, 52 Street E on the east, the Deerfoot Trail on the west and the Seton Boulevard on the south.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Auburn Bay comprise single family homes and townhouses that can cost you as low as around $250,000 or as high as a million and a half for the premium properties.</p>
        </div>
